    <intervention_type>Procedure</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>2D Mammogram</intervention_name>
    <description>Those patients randomized to the mammogram arm will receive a regular 2D mammogram. Compression lasts several seconds in order to obtain 4 views. The x-ray tube is programmed to obtain an arc of low dose projection images through the breast.</description>
    <arm_group_label>A: routine 2D mammogram</arm_group_label>
